Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.99,0:00:10.37,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Colorless!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.37,0:00:13.24,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Not jobless {\i1}(mushoku){\i0}, \Nbut colorless {\i1}(mushoku){\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.56,0:00:15.20,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,I would like a job, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:18.17,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Everything I touch turns white.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.17,0:00:20.70,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Let it all turn white!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.14,0:00:24.27,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,I am the White Bear Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:26.68,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Want me to turn you colorless, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.68,0:00:29.66,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Colorless, colorless!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.66,0:00:30.46,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.85,0:00:33.72,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Hold it, White Bear Monster, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:35.31,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,There's nowhere to stand, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.57,0:00:37.14,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:38.82,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.82,0:00:40.71,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,You idiot! You slow turtle!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.71,0:00:41.97,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm more like a rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.45,0:00:43.83,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,And I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.83,0:00:45.64,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,My muscles are going to be sore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:49.31,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Anyway, that aside, where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:12.59,Title2,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fad(1,459)}Komugi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:12.59,Title3,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fad(1,459)}R
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.77,0:01:13.15,Title1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,459)}Nurse Witch
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:28.02,next ep title - pink,,0,0,0,,Yuto's Fruitless \NRomantic Endeavor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.68,0:02:33.43,Main - Top,YUTO,0,0,0,,This feels wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:35.96,towels for filming,TEXT,0,0,0,,"We are using towels due to filming."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.43,0:02:37.14,Main - Top,YUTO,0,0,0,,It's a bit hot, but it warms \Nme up from head to toe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:40.39,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,It's good for people who get cold easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:43.01,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,I'm impressed. This is an excellent hot spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:44.43,Main,AD,0,0,0,,Okay, cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:47.52,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,Yuto, you're stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:50.86,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,Kokona-chan and Tsukasa-kun, \Nyou're both sort of stiff, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.86,0:02:54.62,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Sorry. This is my first hot spring report.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:56.77,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,I need comments from the \Nbottom of your hearts that say,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.77,0:02:58.61,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,"I'm so glad I came to this hot spring!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:02.59,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,Comments that will leave an \Nimpression on our viewers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.59,0:03:05.16,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,You know, like a cry from the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.65,0:03:08.15,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,This is pretty hard, huh, Tsukasa-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:10.66,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,It's difficult in a different way than dramas are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:12.76,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,Let's try that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:15.24,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,Naturally! From the bottom of your hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:19.67,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,Make viewers desperately want to come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:20.56,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:21.43,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,We'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:23.14,Main,AD,0,0,0,,Camera's rolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:27.64,towels for filming,TEXT,0,0,0,,"We are using towels due to filming."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:26.63,Main - Top,YUTO,0,0,0,,This feels great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.63,0:03:27.89,Main - Top,YUTO,0,0,0,,It's so warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.23,0:03:30.92,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,Yuto, you're still stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.59,0:03:35.48,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:39.78,Main,AD,0,0,0,,Who knows? Perhaps it's a bear \Nthat's come out of hibernation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:40.90,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,A bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:43.54,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:56.50,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,A... A hot spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.10,0:03:57.80,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Ko...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.44,0:04:01.01,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,Komugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.44,0:04:01.01,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,Komugi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.94,0:04:08.68,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Hot... spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:10.83,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,It's a hot spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:14.22,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I feel alive again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.22,0:04:17.60,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I wandered for 562 kilometers in the mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:20.09,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,562. In other words, "Ko-mu-gi"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:20.83,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.83,0:04:23.28,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,A hot spring after a long walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:27.07,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,The exquisitely perfect temperature \Nof the water loosens my stiff muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:28.55,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,The arm I hit when I tripped,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:32.45,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,and the pain of my twisted ankle, \Nall melt away into the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:34.90,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Furthermore, the velvety water seems like
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:37.09,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,it'll make my skin nice and smooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.09,0:04:39.46,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Now this is true happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.97,0:04:40.46,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Lick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.02,0:04:43.80,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Slightly salty... It's a salt water spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:47.18,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Not only can you bathe in it, but I bet \Ndrinking it would be good for anemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:50.85,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Oh, you shouldn't drink it if you've \Ngot high blood pressure, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:54.53,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I'm alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.95,0:05:01.11,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,Okay, cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:02.70,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Yes, cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:03.36,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:04.41,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:06.74,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Yu-nii? Kokona-chan? Tsukasa-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:07.95,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Matsukawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:09.07,Main,MATSU,0,0,0,,I'm moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:10.11,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Goto-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.11,0:05:12.20,Main,GOTO,0,0,0,,Now I want to get in the hot spring, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:14.23,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,When did you guys get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:17.26,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,Boy, that was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:19.34,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,You're Komugi-chan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:21.68,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think you're Komugi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:24.30,Main,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,That was a perfect hot spring report!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:26.43,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Yes, sir! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.77,0:05:29.27,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,It really did feel great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:32.43,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Hot springs are awesome. Right, \NKokona-chan, Tsukasa-kun, and Yu-nii?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:33.89,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.19,0:05:36.35,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,So, Komugi, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:37.78,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I was chasing a mon—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:38.33,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:40.81,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I got lost taking a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:43.72,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,A walk? This far into the mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:46.55,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I just got so caught up in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:49.68,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm glad we're \Nstaying the night together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:50.69,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:52.58,pelican,,0,0,0,,Pelican
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.24,0:05:56.81,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Girly yukatas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:05:59.25,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Wow, Kokona-chan, you look so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:02.28,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Yours is perfect for your \Nenergetic character, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:04.33,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Hooray! Hooray, hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.33,0:06:06.72,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Wait, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:10.34,Main,,0,0,0,,What an outrage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:09.65,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,Tsukasa-han, do you have a moment, nyan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:10.34,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:16.02,Main,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:18.92,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,Don't you think something smells fishy, nyan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:20.60,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Fishy? What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:22.18,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,Komugi-chan, nyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:24.45,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,She claims she was walking \Nthis deep in the mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:27.65,Main,NEKO,0,0,0,,And wasn't she about to say "monster" earlier, nyan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:28.90,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Huh? So you're saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:32.78,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,Is it possible that Komugi-chan \Nis a Tombo-E Girl, nyan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:35.53,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Komugi? Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.53,0:06:38.79,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,There's no way. She just got \Nlost while taking a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:40.41,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,You're right, nyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.41,0:06:42.73,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,That girl as a Tombo-E Girl is just nyat possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:44.99,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Tsukasa-chan, is someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:45.80,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.04,0:06:47.55,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,What's up, Kokona?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.35,0:06:51.76,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I thought I'd go buy some drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:53.31,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,I'll go with you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.31,0:06:56.24,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,That's okay. You can wait in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:58.48,cold,,0,0,0,,Cold
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:01.55,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,What? Komugi-chan, a Tombo-E Girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:03.34,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,That's right, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:05.25,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,Don't you find her suspicious, poko?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:07.03,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,That's what you wanted to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:10.48,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,There's no way. She just got \Nlost while taking a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.72,0:07:12.63,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,I suppose you're right, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:14.74,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,There's no way she is, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:23.71,Main - Italics,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Komugi, a Tombo-E Girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:28.57,Main - Italics,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:30.20,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:31.50,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:34.26,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,I was just thinking how cute that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:36.52,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,You can try it on later, Tsukasa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:37.72,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:39.06,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,After everyone's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:40.51,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Secretly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:41.85,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:44.35,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:45.72,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:48.65,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Oops, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:50.80,Main - Italics,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Komugi-chan is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:52.04,Main - Italics,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:55.37,Main - Italics,KOKONA,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:57.48,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Oh, dinner's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.48,0:07:58.63,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.63,0:08:01.71,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:01.71,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.46,0:08:03.87,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Thanks for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:06.13,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,That was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:06.13,Main - Top,DIRECTOR,0,0,0,,I can't drink anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:07.61,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'm stuffed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:10.38,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,The meat was cut so huge! Right, Yu-nii?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.66,0:08:12.55,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Yeah. I ate too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:14.26,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,We sure ate a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:16.76,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Okay, let's play some ping pong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:18.28,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Ping pong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.55,0:08:20.04,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,To help us digest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:23.19,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Okay, Tsukasa and Kokona will be one team.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:25.56,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Komugi and I will be the other in this match.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:26.73,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,A match?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.10,0:08:29.82,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,The losing team buys the \Nwinning team ice pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:30.66,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:33.80,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Sure. I haven't played ping pong in ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:34.32,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:37.61,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Ice pops! Ice pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.27,0:08:37.61,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Only if you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.19,0:08:40.24,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Yu-nii, that hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.46,0:08:42.30,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:43.54,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Hey, you did it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:45.79,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Okay, let's get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:48.29,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Lightning Smash!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:56.31,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Yu-nii, you're so strong and fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:01.00,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Tsukasa-kun is strong and fast, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.69,0:09:02.18,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:03.81,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:07.11,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,A-Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.07,0:09:08.73,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.94,0:09:15.36,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:31.06,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,That was a good match.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:32.50,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Thanks for the ice pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:37.05,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Yuu-nii, I want an ice pop, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:38.59,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,The losers have to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:40.57,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Ice pop! Ice pop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.57,0:09:42.51,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Jeez, okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:43.89,vending,,0,0,0,,Pick Up Here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:45.15,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.15,0:09:46.10,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.66,0:09:50.98,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,It's yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:52.57,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Yu-nii, you want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.87,0:09:55.36,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,I'm the one who bought it, but okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:58.25,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:09:59.71,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:03.40,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,What flavor did you guys get?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:06.15,Main - Italics,YUTO,0,0,0,,Tsukasa seems dissatisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.15,0:10:08.23,Main - Italics,YUTO,0,0,0,,I need to do something for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:11.44,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Okay, let's test our courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:13.00,Main,ALL,0,0,0,,Test our courage?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:18.33,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,We'll walk a lap around the mountain out back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.63,0:10:20.93,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Hooray! Test of courage, test of courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:25.08,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,There might be bears who have \Nwoken up from hibernation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:29.94,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,How about Komugi and me \Nversus Tsukasa and Kokona?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:32.47,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,We'll leave first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.47,0:10:34.94,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,You guys leave five minutes after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:35.93,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:36.86,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:38.62,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Let's go, Komugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:39.20,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:42.61,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Don't stand so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.61,0:10:45.60,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,But it's so dark, I can't see where I'm walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:48.20,Main - Italics,YUTO,0,0,0,,Tsukasa, you can look forward to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:50.24,Main - Italics,YUTO,0,0,0,,I'll create an opportunity for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.24,0:10:53.34,Main - Italics,YUTO,0,0,0,,A huge opportunity to make \Nthings work out with Kokona.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.60,0:11:21.01,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Are you scared, Komugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:23.00,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,No way... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:25.28,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Maybe we'll see a C.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:27.62,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,A C-C-C?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:31.75,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,C... C...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:33.04,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,C...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:34.37,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.37,0:11:36.80,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Even the Cs you hate so much \Nare hibernating right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.99,0:11:39.00,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Jeez, Yu-nii!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:40.08,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Komugi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.69,0:11:42.86,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,I sense a monster nearby, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.81,0:11:45.93,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,I know you can't see it, but my ears
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:48.22,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,are standing at attention, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:50.45,Main - Italics,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Wh-What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.29,0:11:52.27,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:53.69,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:56.92,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I need to go to the bathroom, \NI forgot my smartphone,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:59.17,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,and I forgot to set my VCR.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:01.30,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'm going back to the inn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:02.32,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.39,0:12:05.45,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:07.62,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,I'll do it myself, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:13.37,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,When Kokona and Tsukasa get here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:14.39,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:16.04,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:17.17,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:20.42,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,She's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:25.30,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,It's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:27.39,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm ready for you anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:32.34,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,This is pretty creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:33.81,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:36.33,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,I sense a monster, poko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:36.81,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:38.66,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,I sense a monster, nyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:52.66,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I'm a bit tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.96,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Tsukasa-chan, could you go on ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:56.46,Main - Italics,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I need to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:57.89,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,O-Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.89,0:13:00.21,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll go on ahead, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:02.09,Main - Italics,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Or I can't transform.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:07.18,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,It's sticking straight out, poko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:09.61,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,As you can see, it's standing at attention, poko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:11.56,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:13.22,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,This way, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:20.46,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,I finally get some screen time! Colorless!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:22.65,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Wait! Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:25.48,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Quit lollygagging and defeat him, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:27.43,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Get my color back, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:29.82,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Why did you let the monster attack you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.82,0:13:31.08,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Shut up, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:32.29,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,I was just a bit slow, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:35.69,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,I'm the colorless and transparent bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:37.71,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I said wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:39.79,Main - Italics,YUTO,0,0,0,,Here they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:41.88,Main - Italics,YUTO,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:47.99,Main - Italics,YUTO,0,0,0,,A b-bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:50.76,Main - Italics,YUTO,0,0,0,,Tsukasa's alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:52.52,Main - Top,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Try to roar like a bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.27,0:13:52.82,Main - Italics,YUTO,0,0,0,,Then I should...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:13:59.04,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,This spot should be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:00.88,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,Nyan! Now turn into a Tombo-E Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.88,0:14:01.94,Main,TUSKASA,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:10.53,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Yu—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.77,0:14:11.85,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Don't make a sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:15.10,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:18.78,Main - Italics,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Y-Yuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.78,0:14:20.17,Main - Italics,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,What? What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:27.07,Main - Italics,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Yuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:28.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:31.69,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Did that hurt? Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:34.60,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Was I poking you with my flashlight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.30,0:14:36.92,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Flashlight...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.01,0:14:40.01,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,We should be okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:42.45,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,There was a bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:45.91,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,We'd be in trouble if it found us,\Nso I was trying to keep you quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:47.28,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:49.80,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,S-So that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.27,0:14:55.22,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,So that's why! You surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:14:58.99,Main - Italics,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Ba-dum...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.87,0:14:59.87,DOKI,FX,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(1,722)}Ba-dum
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:11.89,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Where are Komugi and Kokona?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:20.14,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Low-flying life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.76,0:15:23.27,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,That was close. That nearly got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:24.61,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:25.36,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Uh-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.74,0:15:28.96,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Use your Super Ram and Jam \NKaboosh: From Top to Bottom,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:31.35,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Front to Back, and Diagonally Above Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.35,0:15:32.36,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I'll do that, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:34.98,Main - Top,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Something-or-other Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:36.95,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,The Super Ram and Jam \NKaboosh: From Top to Bottom,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:39.62,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,Front to Back, and Diagonally \NAbove Beam is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.92,0:15:43.79,Main - Italics,NARRATION,0,0,0,,Explaining it would take too long, \Nso I'll leave it up to your imaginations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:47.69,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,A bear without color is a bear without a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.69,0:15:50.53,Main,MONSTER,0,0,0,,Pooh and pooh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:53.80,hello book,,0,0,0,,{\fad(863,1)}Fun Jobs\NFull of Smiles
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:59.06,yoshida clinic,,0,0,0,,White \NBear \NMonster
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.71,0:15:59.06,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Yeah! My color is back, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:01.43,Main,UPSA,0,0,0,,The Fan-C Card is ours, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:03.85,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Komugi-chan, you were useful for once, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:06.28,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Our collection of Fan-C Cards \Nis getting pretty big, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.28,0:16:08.32,Main,USAP,0,0,0,,Princess-P, just you wait, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:13.95,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,We're too late, poko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:16.59,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,The Magical Nurse beat us to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.59,0:16:19.83,Main,TANUP,0,0,0,,But why her, poko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.55,0:16:22.41,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Is Komugi-chan all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:25.03,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,She said she was coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:26.25,sign,,0,0,0,,Danger!!\NEnter at\NOwn Risk
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.03,0:16:26.25,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Did she get lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.59,0:16:29.52,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,I hope she didn't run into \Nany monsters or bears.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:31.64,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,The monster's presence has disappeared, nyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:33.05,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,Someone must've beaten it, nyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:34.34,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:35.88,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:39.17,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Sorry to make you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:41.28,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I got lost again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:44.52,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:50.68,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Singing a song through your nostrils...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:51.52,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,This feels nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.52,0:16:52.30,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:54.43,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Is it a bit hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:16:55.70,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:58.66,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,But maybe it's a little cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.96,0:16:59.70,Main,TSUAKSA,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:06.47,Main - Italics,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Yuto is pretty strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.47,0:17:08.33,Main - Italics,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,He really is a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:11.87,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,You like Yuto-san, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:12.59,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:13.96,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:14.98,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:17.63,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Eh... What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:20.93,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I thought you might.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.93,0:17:22.31,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,I-I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.55,0:17:25.09,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,No, I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:27.85,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,I... you... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.22,0:17:32.59,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I knew for sure after watching you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.59,0:17:35.49,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,That you actually are very girly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:40.74,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,But you've got your fans, \Nyour agency, and your persona.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:43.75,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,There are a lot of difficult things to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:45.98,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I was worried about a lot of things, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:47.33,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Like when I ran that marathon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.45,0:17:50.90,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,And I know one other thing for sure now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:53.97,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Tsukasa-chan, you like Yuto-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:17:58.68,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:01.62,Main - Top,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Go! Go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.84,0:18:04.18,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I think Yuto-san only thinks of \NKomugi-chan as a sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:04.18,Main - Top,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Over there. Over where?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:06.36,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.36,0:18:07.20,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:10.52,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,And I'm not totally sure, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.47,0:18:14.53,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I think he really cares about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:20.57,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,So it's okay. You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:25.83,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Splash!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.18,0:18:30.65,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Hey, Komugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.91,0:18:32.62,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,What were you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.62,0:18:34.28,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Half of it is a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.28,0:18:34.96,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:36.36,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Half?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:38.00,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,The other half is that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:41.68,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Tsukasa-chan is actually really girly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:44.35,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Huh? Kokona-chan, you knew, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:45.51,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:49.23,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Hey, when we get back to our room...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.55,0:18:56.94,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Well, Tsukasa-chan, Komugi-chan \Nand I are getting out first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:18:58.75,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.55,0:18:59.20,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Just come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:03.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Nyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:05.89,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,The water's nice, nyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:09.89,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,My tongue is sensitive to heat, \Nbut I do like hot springs, nyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.89,0:19:10.55,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:13.25,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Y-Yuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:15.00,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Tsukasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:16.96,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Is someone else there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:20.80,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,I... It's just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:22.19,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.50,0:19:27.22,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Sorry about earlier. Things got a little hectic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:29.36,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,I wanted you and Kokona...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.36,0:19:30.57,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:33.52,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,I just wanted you to have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:38.53,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,You always want your friends to have fun
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:40.03,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,and be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:45.45,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Friends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:48.84,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,How happy, but also sad for Tsukasa-han, nyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:54.51,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,I appreciate the thought. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:56.22,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,I did have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.22,0:19:58.15,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Yeah. It wasn't bad at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:00.59,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,Really? That's good, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:02.03,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.52,0:20:06.18,Main,NEKOP,0,0,0,,Tsukasa-han...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.49,0:20:09.80,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,It sure is pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:10.46,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.99,0:20:11.77,Main,YUTO,0,0,0,,The moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:14.52,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:21.46,Main - Italics,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Yuto...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:25.39,Main - Italics,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Yuto and I are looking and the same moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:00.17,pelican,,0,0,0,,Pelican
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.73,0:22:02.55,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:04.05,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,Take it off! Take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.43,0:22:08.34,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.34,0:22:10.01,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,It looks great on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.32,0:22:11.80,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.80,0:22:16.39,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,It's not fair that you look good whether\Nyou dress masculine or feminine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.01,0:22:17.95,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.95,0:22:20.81,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,I made a promise with Tsukasa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.81,0:22:21.81,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,A promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.09,0:22:24.48,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,That you, Tsukasa-chan, and I
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.48,0:22:27.70,Main,KOMUGI,0,0,0,,would someday sing together \Nat the Tokyo Skydome.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.70,0:22:28.96,Main,KOKONA,0,0,0,,That sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.96,0:22:30.47,Main,TSUKASA,0,0,0,,Yeah, the three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.95,0:22:39.96,Next Time,TEXT,0,0,0,,Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.58,0:22:36.66,Main,KOHARU,0,0,0,,Koharu here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.66,0:22:39.96,Main,KOHARU,0,0,0,,I'm awaiting your requests \Nfor character lunches.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:41.72,Main,KOHARU,0,0,0,,The next episode is \N"Goodbye, Komugi-chan."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.96,0:22:43.71,next ep title,TEXT,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Komugi-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.72,0:22:43.71,Main,KOHARU,0,0,0,,Wait, what? Is it the final episode?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.71,0:22:47.39,Main,KOHARU,0,0,0,,Starting next week is the new show, \N{\i1}Magical Character Lunch Koharu-san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.71,0:22:49.97,Next Time,TEXT,0,0,0,,Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.39,0:22:49.62,Main,KOHARU,0,0,0,,Nah, not really. I'm only joking.